query.prompt:
Please translate each line literally into English and Old English.
142 Nepote ho io di là c’ha nome Alagia, 143 buona da sé, pur che la nostra casa 144 non faccia lei per essempro malvagia;
145 e questa sola di là m’è rimasa».

query.result:
**English:**
142 I have a granddaughter there whose name is Alagia, 143 good in herself, provided that our household 144 does not make her wicked by its example;
145 and she alone is left to me from there.
